metadata.name: Bones of the Sea
metadata.description:
Somewhere far away where solitude meets tranquillity, exhibited in a museum, you might contemplate what seems to be the Bones of the Sea. Beyond the reach of our understanding, something had fed, slept, lived and met its end.

Original 3D generative art, fully procedurals textures.
Created the 24th October 2021.
Resolution: 4000 x 4000
